features: ELIMINATES ODORS FOR UP TO 90 DAYS - The Odor Eliminator Gel Beads will continue to neutralize and eliminate odors for up to 90 days in up to 450 square feet. Each Gel Bead will leave behind a light and pleasant fragrance that is not overpowering.

MADE WITH ESSENTIAL OILS - Each Odor Eliminator Gel Bead contains 12 Ounces of product. The products are made with plant derived ingredients and formulated with a blend of essential oil based fragrances which adds a distinct and unforgettable aroma to any area you place and use the jar.
MADE IN THE USA - Every Odor Neutralizing Gel Bead is proudly Made in the USA.

SAFE AND EFFECTIVE FORMULA - Our Gel Beads were developed with safety in mind. Simply remove the top label and open the jar to remove the interior liner and screw the cap back on. For maximum effectiveness, place in a well ventilated area.

USE ANYWHERE RECURRING ODORS ARE A PROBLEM - Use the Gel Beads in your home, bathroom, closet, office, RV, boat etc. to remove odors from smoke, garbage cans, pet areas, food and anywhere recurring odors are a problem.

It is formulated to be safe and effective. How should I use the product? To use, simply remove the lid and inner lid liner, before replacing lid and placing where the odor problem exists. The Odor Eliminator will continually work 24/7 for up to 90 days in 450 square feet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My to go deodorizer
reviews.reviewText: I have These on subscription and Love how effective they are in the restroom. The subtle fragrance leaves the space feeling fresh. Highly recommended.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The fragrance isn’t real strong and lasts a long time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Scent a little overwhelming at first but rapidly fades to background while removing the offending odors. The beads shrink over time - you’ll know when to order more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Do not know how long this product is effective.
reviews.reviewText: The "Fresh Linen" scent seems to have lasted only three days but the "beads" seem to continue to tame bathroom odor! If the beads continue to work effectively for 60-90 days, as advertised, I can live with it even if the "Fresh Linen" scent is gone. The scent is only detectable if I put my nose to the jar. But that is not how it should work.I hope I am not being unfair to this product, especially if a small company is involved. Unfortunately, we are asked to review a product almost the moment we receive it. If I am missing something, I would appreciate hearing from someone else who has purchased this item and has a different experience with it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No odors in my house❗️
reviews.reviewText: I like these deodorizing beads a lot. I keep a fresh supply on hand all the time to replace when needed. My house doesn’t have odors and I use the linen and cotton ones so there are no heavy perfume smells. Try them…

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Disappointed with Odor Eliminator Gel Beads
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased a couple of boxes of these Odor Eliminator Gel Beads, hoping to tackle some persistent odors in my home. Unfortunately, the results were far from satisfactory.Despite following the instructions diligently, the gel beads did not seem to make any significant difference in clearing up the unpleasant smells. I had high hopes for this product, but it simply didn't deliver on its promise.To make matters worse, when I decided to return the boxes, I encountered an issue. The top paper cover on one of the boxes was missing, making the return process more complicated. It's frustrating when a product not only fails to live up to expectations but also presents challenges when attempting to seek a refund.I'm disappointed with my experience and would caution others considering these Odor Eliminator Gel Beads to think twice before making a purchase. The missing cover added an extra layer of inconvenience, making this overall a regrettable buy for me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works on even strong odors!
reviews.reviewText: My closet unfortunately is above the kitchen, so all the smells of cooking stick to my clothes and linger. I don’t love going into work smelling like garlic lol. I put 1 of these in my closet and all of my clothes no longer have that smell of cooking. Now they smell like freshly washed clothes again. Definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars No bang for your buck
reviews.reviewText: Put two of these out in an average size one bedroom apartment and a few days later noticed you could hardly smell anything unless you were within four feet of the things, took the perforated lid off and it improved some. Really disappointed with the performance of these for the money.

reviews.reviewTitle: A good product at a reasonable price
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been using this product for some time….I have a musty basement issue…My home office and man/den are down there….For many years I used spray products that only lasted for a short time…What I like about this Clear Air method is that it’s not an exaggerated scent…I just open the lid and it quietly defeats the musty smell for a good long time …
fast delivery and real happy with my purchase
It does a wonderful job, just be carefull not to use too much!
Liked the scent but they were leaking in the package
